'''雙手交叉的女人'''（''Femme aux Bras Croisés''）是[[畢加索|畢加索]]畫於1902年的油畫，其主題未知，但其中的女子可能是巴黎圣拉扎爾監獄醫院中的犯人。<ref name=inmate>{{cite news|url=http://www.iht.com/articles/2000/11/10/post.t_5.php|title=AUCTIONS : A Picasso Record|author=Melikian, Souren|date=2000-11-10|publisher=International Herald Tribune|accessdate=2013-08-21|archive-date=2008-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080226184158/http://www.iht.com/articles/2000/11/10/post.t_5.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==歷史==

[[格特鲁德·斯泰因|格特鲁德·斯泰因]]是最初從畢加索手裡買下這幅畫的人。自1936年開始由[[昌西·麥考密克|昌西·麥考密克]]的家族收藏，並被租借給[[芝加哥藝術學院|芝加哥藝術學院]]<ref>{{cite news |title= Picasso Auction Record: $55 Million |date= November 9, 2000 |author= Carol Vogel |newspaper= [[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |url= http://www.nytimes.com/2000/11/09/nyregion/picasso-auction-record-55-million.html |accessdate= January 2, 2011 |archive-date= 2019-12-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191204005211/https://www.nytimes.com/2000/11/09/nyregion/picasso-auction-record-55-million.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。
2000年在紐約[[佳士得|佳士得]]以5500萬美元的價格被人買走。<ref name=sale>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/low/entertainment/926736.stm|publisher=BBC News Online|date=2000-09-15|title=Picasso for sale - a snip at £16m|accessdate=2013-08-21|archive-date=2007-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071016124355/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/low/entertainment/926736.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

